metadata.name: Abandoned Latent Places #0 #1/100
metadata.description:
“The swing still hangs from the old oak tree  
A place where memories were made, now just a memory  
But the wind still sings through the broken glass  
A ghostly whisper in the AI latent space, alas”

Every corner of the AI latent space is an abandoned place, until someone reveals it through AI art. 
A free-to-mint preview of the upcoming RTX AI photography collection.
